{"tid":1483634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［遊行靜坐後，和理非升級］823 人鏈！823 人鏈！","createTime":"2019-08-18T12:35:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T03:36:02.000Z","uid":112094,"like":45,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"6327a72362d4396c2e85033493e2be53ce48eab2","tid":1483634,"uid":112094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T12:35:18.000Z","msg":"之前有巴打同Facebook講過，不過沉咗底，我再開post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>知唔知今個星期五係咩日子？係波羅的海之路三十周年！！！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Baltic_Way#/media/File%3ABaltsk%C3%BD%C5%98et%C4%9Bz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FBaltic_Way%23%2Fmedia%2FFile%253ABaltsk%25C3%25BD%25C5%2598et%25C4%259Bz.jpg&h=cd577ef4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單啲講，二戰時期希特拉同斯大林秘密簽定協議將波羅的海三小國（立陶宛、拉脫維亞和愛沙尼亞）劃入蘇聯勢力範圍，經過長年抗爭，三個國家嘅人民喺當年蘇聯嘅民主化浪潮中發起一次組人鏈嘅活動。<br />\n<br />\n喺1989年8月23號傍晚七點，組成超過650公里嘅人鏈連接三個國家嘅首都，以抗議蘇聯嘅非法佔領。媒體爭相報導呢次抗爭，更直接導致波羅的海三國率先脫離蘇聯加盟國身分獨立，算係和理非成功爭取嘅一例。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今個星期五就係8月23號，時間嚟到三十年後嘅香港</span>，過去兩個月抗爭揭露中共港共打壓香港人嘅殘暴一面，如果我哋要以受害人身分向國際求助，就需要非常上鏡吸引報導嘅抗爭手法，仲可以連結多三個國家。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n具體做法：星期五放工後一齊去唔同地鐵站出口，向前後一個站方向組人鏈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">港島</span>就沿電車路<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">荃灣線</span>就彌敦道駁長沙灣道再上荔景去荃灣<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">觀塘線</span>就龍翔道駁觀塘道。<br />\n<br />\n好處：方便/ 和平 / 冇咁阻街/ 有影響力/ 畫面靚/ 接觸面廣/ 參與度高<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n東歐國家、蘇聯國內和臺灣都相繼舉行過類似示威，如2004年約有200萬臺灣民眾參與的228百萬人手牽手護台灣。<br />\n<br />\n連2016年周融都試過號召五千人上山頂，喺太平山頂手牽手，參加「正能量　團結太平山」活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［和理非升級］一生人一次嘅機會嚟喇！！！！想唔想上Buzzfeed 9GAG？！？！？！？！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475842\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475842</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook post<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10156092700521504&amp;id=507126503\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10156092700521504%26id%3D507126503&d=xzf4O3tGv54ZmzQe4QccrICLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=1d8eb667\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10156092700521504&amp;id=507126503</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"6b48e8d319001d7272de4d6a6dca22e402f29b6e","tid":1483634,"uid":112094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T12:36:33.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92c33937783de7838faf74cbe6254c588112ea22","tid":1483634,"uid":112094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T12:36:49.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f559e1d27df0c35e78fd39350dc8a650cdda3ef","tid":1483634,"uid":112094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T12:37:16.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2047fdea1beb50ca983cd1c468885ef824d8a27d","tid":1483634,"uid":53349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"20