運動將來可能分裂，凝聚民間對於「五大訴求缺一不可」嘅共識，係文宣重中之重嘅長期目標<br />\n<br />\n#今次逆權運動香港人只許勝不許敗，否則新疆模式一定會搬過黎香港實行，<span style=\"color: red;\">以中共性格，當一個地方出現亂事之後，中共喺平亂之後一定會再嚴格十倍管治呢個地方</span>，呢場仗一輸社會信用計分制度好快就會實行<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">#毋忘葉虎事件！（疑似中聯辦指揮黑社會打人）大家可以幫推，甚至可以做埋社區文宣煲大佢，絕對唔可以比呢單野不了了之！</span><br />\n［緊急］點解葉虎單嘢可以不了了之？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382778\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382778</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ffb72eb6b4c8b4f7536e642c67994ef0cbe89719","tid":1483634,"uid":301360,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T12:58:43.000Z","msg":"一定去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c98ac8d6f41ace61b8e86161ed46b9c29f99495b","tid":1483634,"uid":29899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T13:26:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dca00fdc8257c32b750eef3e034af79bb9830f29","tid":1483634,"uid":235374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T13:27:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"482a0ea8155869c9d933a24a4078dcd24be2ab5d","tid":1483634,"uid":300768,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T13:31:47.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"4aa1238216e24e8d80cb2a34bd060d6a62194156","tid":1483634,"uid":49754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:26:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1e78e24abbea4a8644d4ab46b4807d28cd0e96a4","tid":1483634,"uid":297657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:33:21.000Z","msg":"推823"},{"pid":"cf6df33e81e46e512eec63418952e4416d15a354","tid":1483634,"uid":297657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:33:47.000Z","msg":"推呀大家 時間唔多"},{"pid":"7531d6bf99f08a5c1c932ed49c40b7c0f64376f2","tid":1483634,"uid":175424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:54:46.000Z","msg"